    "Allocating specific roles to the AI agent and to the trainee nurse within a framework of expected responses enabled the narrative to resemble an authentic interaction, but within a safe environment.",
    "Prompting the AI agent to progress the narrative under specific conditions and to provide structured feedback to students, enabled a cohesive educational experience that was able to address specific gaps in student knowledge of neonatal practice and procedure.",
    "Staff and student feedback demonstrated positive results in terms of engagement, satisfaction, academic performance and student well-being."
